{"tid":2047384,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE子瑜低胸中空裙太短！熱舞「狂洩深溝、腿根黑影」引暴動","createTime":"2020-06-02T05:18:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T08:24:42.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"e84ce3ffcadcf05837dcb1bdcdce2c49777d3091","tid":2047384,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T05:18:38.000Z","msg":"南韓女團TWICE在6/1晚間發表全新單曲《MORE &amp; MORE》，之後更進行LIVE線上直播發表會與粉絲們互動並帶來熱舞。子瑜以一件綠色中空超激短裙驚艷全場，再度引發話題。<br />\n<br />\nTWICE於5月份開始陸續釋出新專輯《MORE &amp; MORE》的預告影片，令粉絲們期待指數破表，終於在6/1正式公開MV後便在短短一天突破千萬點閱，歌曲更立即攻下日本、巴西、加拿大等30個國家的iTunes專輯榜單第一名，可見她們的超高人氣。<br />\n<br />\n當晚，TWICE也開啟直播與粉絲暢聊專輯內容，並在現場帶來新歌熱舞，而子瑜的造型有別於其他團員的波希迷亞風，她穿著綠色的低胸中空短裙在畫面中相當吸睛，而在熱舞的過程中，子瑜裙子疑似太短不停的露出長腿及黑色小褲，令粉絲看得直呼「太辣了」。"},{"pid":"b168b7d5c8c9ddf263a651301eff2e7b883af518","tid":2047384,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T05:18:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2020-06-02/900/20200602003164.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2020-06-02%2F900%2F20200602003164.jpg&h=058fbac6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTWICE子瑜中空裙太短！熱舞「狂洩深溝、腿根黑影」引暴動（圖／YOUTUBE）"},{"pid":"fc85d00bf200487c3db94f8b4118f22764359842","tid":2047384,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T05:19:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/c6f86177134acee308eb9e9e394c3a04/defa20e773e23863-1b/s400x600/b76355944d240dfd7e761920ecddce4cb5c5577c.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2Fc6f86177134acee308eb9e9e394c3a04%2Fdefa20e773e23863-1b%2Fs400x600%2Fb76355944d240dfd7e761920ecddce4cb5c5577c.gifv&h=6b35fe68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/9c0e7c3a8834b8edc44171199b5c1efa/defa20e773e23863-64/s400x600/a6247fa292edfe9645ee18cf2ca2cb7848a8df0d.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%